This is me walking out of 2022, and not looking back!!! Excited for 2023!

Massive CONGRATULATIONS TO SELMA FOR WINNING AT THE @peopleschoice THE PEOPLE HAVE VOTED !!! You are forever part of the @dancingwiththestars @disneyplus family! You have inspired millions of people all around the world, and continue to do so, with all your hard work and dedication. I’m so lucky and grateful that I got to tag along last night, and also be along side you during this DWTS journey that I will never forget, you have inspired me and taught me so much about myself and life. Everyone go and wish @selmablair a CONGRATULATIONS and before I finish a huge congratulations to my brother from another mother @vancityreynolds the man the myth the legend!!! Im writing this like I know him, but honestly I pooped my pants when I saw him and screamed Selma I need a picture, so Selma asked for me and he said “ of course , Sasha Farber” so just saying we are like costars now😂

Can’t believe it’s the last day of tour today with our last two shows. Wow 61 shows traveling around the whole of America on a bus, performing for soooo many sold out venues and meeting so many incredible fans! Sometime I have to pinch myself to make sure this is real and I’m not dreaming! I feel at home when I’m on stage, and this tour was very special for me!!! Thank you to all my fellow dancers on stage, and thank you to @dancingwiththestars for making this dream come true!!! IM GOING TO ROCK THE SHIT OUT OF THESE TWO LAST SHOWS TODAY !!!!! Let’s go !!!!📹: @sarahelizabeth_k
Reunited!!!! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️I snuck in when he had his play time and screamed his name !!!!!!

I can’t believe the tour is over, 61 shows!!!! I had the time of my life, meeting and performing for all of you guys every night!! Thank you to all the crew, and my fellow cast members I’m so lucky that I get to share the stage with the worlds best, and off course thank you @nopenother and @nikolevallins for putting on the best tour!!!!! I miss it already, lets run it back and do it again❤️Until next time!!!! @dwtstourofficial @dancingwiththestars
I haven’t laughed so much In a while!!! When u haven’t seen your friend in a while but when u see them, it’s like no time has gone past!!!

Tonight you danced  beautifully and told a beautiful story through dance and inspired me so much and one day I want  to have that love story❤️ Thank you to everyone who voted and kept us safe we love you soooooo much 🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻 WEEK 6 BABY!!!!

I can’t believe it’s all coming to an end! Tomorrow is the day we dreamed of from day one!!! This show is about growth and that’s what she achieved, and that someone is my partner 🥹🥹🥹🥹 @alysonhannigan THE FINALS ARE TOMORROW!!!!!!
We are having the time of our life and so close to the big dream we need you!!!! Voting is open text Alyson to 21523 x 10 times please please this dream is so close I can touch it!!!!
BIGGGGGG CONGRATULATIONS TO THE WINNERS @_xochitl.gomez @valentin what a season you guys had!!!!! Soooo beautiful to watch you both shine !!!

Well here it is, our last dance!! This is a journey I’ll never forget, I got to transform this incredible woman into the dancer she became, and inbetween gained a friend for life. Alyson broke all the boundaries and hurdles she came in with , and each week was a new challenge for her, but at the end of the day everything was worth it , just so we can do this freestyle!!!!! Alyson has so much heart and soul, and it has been an honor getting to teach her to dance week in week out we laughed we cried but most importantly we had fun.  I love this show soooo much everyone from wardrobe to camera operators, producers, creative, EVERYONE backstage , is the best in the biz!!! I miss it already thank you to everyone who supported us and voted !!! We love you ! Alyson I love you and I’ll see you at the studio on Friday 🤩 Enjoy this freestyle 🎥

I wanted to post this picture and celebrate, how proud and hard working my partner was during the season!!!! I believe dance is the best way to exercise stimulate the brain and have fun in the process!!!!! I call it “BodyBySasha” who wants to sign up !!!!!
Two things I love doing, COOKING & DANCING!!!!!!
